'''Jaime Prieto Amaya''' (June 27, 1941 – August 25, 2010) was the [[Roman Catholic]] bishop of the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Cúcuta]], [[Colombia]].

Ordained in 1965, he became bishop in 1993 and in 2008 was appointed bishop of the Cúcuta Diocese.<ref>{{Catholic-hierarchy|bishop|bpram|Bishop Jaime Prieto Amaya|21 January 2015}}</ref>

